# Dataset Information

> **Note:** The dataset used in this project was **AI-generated** using Claude (Anthropic) to simulate a realistic Southeast Asian B2B sales environment. It is intended purely for learning and portfolio demonstration purposes.

---

## Overview

| Property | Details |
|---|---|
| File | Dataset_Project.xlsx |
| Source | AI-Generated (Claude by Anthropic) |
| Format | Microsoft Excel (.xlsx) |
| Rows | 1,467 order records |
| Columns | 13 fields |
| Time Period | April 2025 – January 2026 |
| Countries | 11 Southeast Asian markets |
| Product Categories | Electronics, Office Equipment, Packaging |

---

## Data Fields

| Column | Description |
|---|---|
| Order ID | Unique order identifier |
| Month | Order month (date format) |
| Country | Destination country — one of 11 Southeast Asian markets in the dataset |
| Customer Name | Buyer/client name |
| Product Category | High-level product grouping (Electronics, Office Equipment, Packaging) |
| Product Name | Specific product sold |
| Quantity | Units sold |
| UOM | Unit of measurement (e.g. pcs, box, kg) |
| Base Price | Price per unit before packing and freight costs |
| Amount in LC | Total revenue value in the destination country's local currency |
| Total Packing Cost | Total packaging cost for the order |
| Total Freight | Total freight/shipping cost for the order |
| Variable Cost per Unit | Variable manufacturing cost per unit |

---

## How This Data Is Used

This dataset is loaded into **Power BI** via Power Query, where it undergoes cleaning and transformation. Custom **DAX measures** are built on top of it to calculate profitability metrics, revenue trends, and country/product-level performance — all visualised in the Sales Analytics Dashboard.

---

## Data Limitations

- Dataset is AI-generated and does not represent real company or customer data
- Intended for learning and portfolio demonstration only
- Currency values across markets are simulated and may not reflect real exchange rates
